{"tid":2489103,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"麻煩飛馬電腦 林仔入一入黎(3)","createTime":"2021-04-14T17:16:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T05:37:27.000Z","uid":205162,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"fd0bf1aab47ce3451ff218fcff19768b0df21728","tid":2489103,"uid":205162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:16:42.000Z","msg":"繼續等飛馬上水<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原post讓治 巴打內容：<br />\n首先希望所有回覆既人追清楚第一個post<br />\n明白發生咩事先<br />\n<br />\n垃撚圾 飛馬電腦 有卡唔派貨 做臭自己個朵<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2483475\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2483475</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNmhVcRQDcusCDBeAxGLQcvFtFZ4gXuFqUv7xxvS7CFv4?filename=mxLAyoc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmxLAyoc.png&h=06be977c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢件事既然你講到咁我都覺得冇乜好討論<br />\n天下烏鴉一樣黑<br />\n好聽啲講飛馬電腦係身不由己<br />\n難聽啲講係同流合污<br />\n唔係之前既飛馬<br />\n<span class=\"red\">只可以講生於香港真係好慘 邊度都有社會既縮影<br />\n電腦界都唔例外</span><br />\n<br />\n撇開腦場文化啲嘢同埋放卡單野<br />\n<br />\n首先真係希望唔好開口埋口連登仔<br />\n一味覺得連登仔唔講道理 <br />\n唔用連登我又何嘗唔係一個電普通腦用家<br />\n你起下底你見我成日用連登咩？<br />\n我就係覺得件事真係好唔公平先放上黎<br />\n同埋都唔係淨係得我一個人放上連登 <br />\n其他討論區明明都有一模一樣嘅事<br />\n點解要針對「連登」？<br />\n<br />\n電腦界嘅人淨係一味識得標籤連登<br />\n我唔否認有激進嘅巴打 但係係咪一個正常人都冇？<br />\n我自問冇HKEPC account <br />\n如果我有ac喺HKEPC po你地會點講？<br />\n我都好清楚講到明係見到放礦卡個post<br />\n我先至將呢件事放上硬件台  sounds fair係咪？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdpvcZu8KNeQoDKTyp7ND6LE74mwmGzao8KXTkWXPPJAy?filename=m6jtTvZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm6jtTvZ.png&h=cfa6a73d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首先禮貌上講返句同林仔唔好意思先 <br />\n其實我唔想拉你同vg落水 <br />\n我自己上兩個post已經講過 <br />\n只係想飛馬電腦回應<br />\n不過其他連登仔一定會屌你地唔出聲<br />\n容我代埋佢哋講一聲唔好意思<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n既得利益（英語：Vested interest）是一種利益衝突，指的是一個人在決策時可能會因為在既有選擇下有機會獲得利益，而偏好這個選項。「既得利益」不一定是現在就已經有的利益，也可能是若制度不變，該人或群體可以得到的。<br />\n<br />\n但係林仔我想講我買唔到卡而出聲嘅時候<br />\n我只不過維護緊我自己嘅權益<br />\n我想問當我喺連登上面開post既時候<br />\n我獲取左啲乜嘢利益或者將來我會獲取啲乜嘢利益<br />\n金錢？名氣？<br />\n<br />\n同埋點解用輿論係有問題？<br />\n我唔係對付緊共產黨<br />\n我放上黎就係要利用輿論<br />\n比其他人知道飛馬電腦做事幾咁不負責任同惡劣<br />\n你咁講係咪真係想個個有事就告鳩啲電腦鋪先安樂？ <br />\n<br />\n我自問問心無愧 <br />\n都唔覺得自己有任何嘢做錯<br />\n用真身自爆埋搵個地方同你討論都冇問題<br />\n如果我炒車柒咗做何生2.0比你哋笑冇問題<br />\n我有cap圖所有WhatsApp記錄都喺度<br />\n我唔明你哋所謂事實嘅全部喺邊度 <br />\n係我隱瞞左啲乜嘢啊定係點啊？<br />\n既然你哋有事實嘅全部咁不如你講嚟聽嚇喇<br />\n都無謂收埋喺patreon <br />\n等其他人以為又老作 飛馬俾人屈<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfHTJHmSvqrR75BzyvKtrXPPNFVHNduBwjpHaByw7Dtsd?filename=b4tnds4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb4tnds4.png&h=b71b71d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n究竟飛馬呢件事嘅處理手法係咪完全冇問題<br />\n點解隔離ctf同法記都有單訂但係人哋已經一早見好就收 處理好曬？<br />\n你明知呢個其實一個計時炸彈黎 <br />\n如果我嗰日睇唔到你個網張卡有貨限砌機<br />\n冇篤爆到你哋<br />\n你係咪打算依家繼續由所有其他訂左卡喺度繼續等<br />\n就算我今日唔講你係咪覺得之後冇事？<br />\n冇第二個人會察覺到？<br />\n全部人一直喺度等你一路等一路等<br />\n你就一直唔派貨唔同人講就算？<br />\n有冇諗過如果今日一個普通人 <br />\n甚至當係細路仔 唔係好瞭解電腦市場淨係鍾意打機<br />\n訂左顯卡 如果佢唔瞭解市況 <br />\n等左四個月你俾人篤爆咗<br />\n本身7899之後你開口劈萬五 你企喺消費者嘅立場<br />\n蝕唔蝕底？<br />\n<span class=\"red\">你以為我冇企係飛馬立場諗？<br />\n我都知你入貨一定貴 <br />\n我都冇逼你7899俾卡我<br />\n我叫你俾個合理價格我<br />\n萬五又係咪真係一個合理嘅價格<br />\n點解法記strix 而家做到11999？<br />\n一定係法記好鍾意蝕錢<br />\n點解你TUF所謂嘅合理價格係15000？<br />\n其實你開萬二 萬三<br />\n已經有唔少客會要張卡 <br />\n係咪開13000你已經賺唔到錢？<br />\n定係想賺埋嗰2000？</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係咪唔需要任何回應唔需要任何公開道歉？<br />\n唔好話我為咗啲咩任何利益而講單嘢出嚟<br />\n我之前俾咗訂都俾咗時間 <br />\n請問我有咩利益？<br />\n你估我真係告鳩飛馬？<br />\n點解做錯事唔可以道歉？<br />\n油耳成個人版係到啦<br />\n我冇要你賠任何野 <br />\n你<span class=\"red\">公開道歉同埋退晒所有訂比番人</span><br />\n我就唔會再煩撚住你 只不過你個朵已經臭晒<br />\n喂Mathew記唔記得你開舖嗰陣時你啲宗旨係咩呀<br />\n我之前有喺法記買過電腦<br />\n點解我要揀喺你到訂先 你自己諗下<br />\n咁而家點解我又要屌你屌飛馬到咁撚樣先<br />\n做買賣唔係淨係睇錢㗎 <br />\n口碑 信譽 良心 服務 有邊樣仲喺度？<br />\n你對唔對得着自己講過嘅嘢呀？<br />\n你官網條片不如唔好再比人睇啦<br />\n真係好核突呀<br />\n你望吓WhatsApp cap圖最後對你哋講乜嘢<br />\n係失望呀好撚失望<br />\n<br />\n最後Facebook上面全部嗰啲廢佬老屎忽口吻啲人真係收收嗲啦<br />\n咩冇見過世面呀 咩冇落腦場做啊 呢類comment<br />\n你哋呢啲就係覺得自己有經驗 做得耐 見得多<br />\n而家連是非黑白都唔識分嗰啲人<br />\n你睇吓自己講嘢同藍絲group啲人幾似啊<br />\n真係好核突啊<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQxs8hJX36tfPjrcoPfYqBsSgLXAv1XVxN8owc3TEkV81?filename=N8y2XS4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN8y2XS4.png&h=d6058fc5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmerCu7kzDrC1nXHAkxxUzYERceC9Gf8vzBi84s1ZSLwSj?filename=kZzQ6Mq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkZzQ6Mq.png&h=8594b505&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"349862c6d424f2a905df9465b45e1298b524ccfc","tid":2489103,"uid":205162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:17:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSGzfdcA8wdUD9WXb9PNTLHossBfvsaGHdtWrk2bmRWfL?filename=oitbhOH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoitbhOH.jpg&h=10069bc9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b5d42fa805cd191d2e03b00671fdbdeb6ea0d239","tid":2489103,"uid":9103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:18:26.000Z","msg":"你都有今日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bee002fa484b987b470445b94bd161f70b90100","tid":2489103,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:18:45.000Z","msg":"召喚讓治巴"},{"pid":"18e4546bd95ad087bd092c372d737fd51e56f39d","tid":2489103,"uid":205162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:18:47.000Z","msg":"搵人整合 雞精<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36e1a7af38483f4411d3418cc14362c8ac3f8d08","tid":2489103,"uid":205162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5d42fa805cd191d2e03b00671fdbdeb6ea0d239","tid":2489103,"uid":9103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:18:26.000Z","msg":"你都有今日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:19:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69083f9ab7c6b26e59d5d845d5325552c87be922","tid":2489103,"uid":128117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:19:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"addaa78f227455f840ea3ec591fd4b03b86929a3","tid":2489103,"uid":9103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36e1a7af38483f4411d3418cc14362c8ac3f8d08","tid":2489103,"uid":205162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5d42fa805cd191d2e03b00671fdbdeb6ea0d239","tid":2489103,"uid":9103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:18:26.000Z","msg":"你都有今日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:19:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:19:55.000Z","msg":"開post個個左下啲紅點迫死強迫症<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbe37bf31ee0ab6cb66ea1edab9aac1aba9ca96e","tid":2489103,"uid":205162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:19:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZ57CGRTpHQSovvziS7eHNcPrisScFf11MmdJX13pKkmC?filename=iONCXPA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiONCXPA.jpg&h=4696de96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d8ae37d7656d156eb044d94fc1f15c68dd5c651","tid":2489103,"uid":119478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:20:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"125622acfc5de2ad4a6f907bf043325af4c61d59","tid":2489103,